        "setup": "Go to the [Developer portal](https://www.notion.so/developers) and create a new personal access token. Choose a token name, the workspace it belongs to, and the capabilities you need. Use this for personal scripts, CLI workflows, and Workers when you want to act as yourself. The token is used as `Authorization: Bearer <token>` and is also accepted by the Notion CLI via `NOTION_API_TOKEN`.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
      "notion_internal_token": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "label": "Internal connection installation access token",
